data.description: Give me land!! This is the perfect spot if you are wanting some space and room to roam! 4 large bedrooms, 3 bath house with large living area, home office, pool and shop! Beautiful kitchen with tons of storage and countertops + a huge laundry room! The updated kitchen has a ton of storage, granite counters, custom cabinets and is open to dining and living! Original 2 car was converted to second master suite with bath and closets! Texas sized pool & patio w/ block fenced yard! Nice landscaping!
